{"title":"红枫·伞","authors":["萧韶光"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":10,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"红枫·伞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"萧韶光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史老人告诉我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三湾枫树坪那棵红枫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像毛泽东当年那把红油纸伞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋风秋雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙吟虎啸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那年，镰刀与斧头铿锵作响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一队闹秋收暴动的血性汉子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着放弃攻城的疑虑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟随一位撑红油纸伞的书生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从文家市出发"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向罗霄山脉中段走来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别无选择"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当“山大王”去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东认准了这条路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屈指十日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直抵三湾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红枫如火形似伞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伞下，毛泽东用独特的方式"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清点脊梁与灵魂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整编理想与信念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将镰刀与斧头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"组成一个图案"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连同一个阶级的命运"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高高举过头顶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，一支新型的人民军队"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开始整齐地呼吸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东手掂枫叶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一张草图上牵出一道彩虹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他用五指朝图上一扣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恰好扣成黄洋界、朱砂冲、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双马石、八面山、桐木岭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五大哨口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走，上山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷鸣中，红油纸伞一挥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"令大小城市打了个寒战"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他踏出的第一个脚印"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成了中国历史崭新的起点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东与朱德"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于在这里握手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"握得地动山颠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"握出星火霹雳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东用绑腿丈量五百里井冈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丈量中华民族的前途"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丈量反动派的末日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蘸着火与血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋笔如风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写下“星星之火，可以燎原”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那把红油纸伞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为华夏故园遮风挡雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伞上，滚滴民族的泪珠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滑落历史痛苦的呻吟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矢志不移"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要将艳阳天高高撑起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直到西柏坡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他掸了掸征尘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依旧像位书生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依旧挟着红油纸伞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻松地说了句"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进京赶考去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦！以农村包围城市"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最后夺取全国胜利"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东在天安门城楼上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于给历史亮出标准答案"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五百里井冈山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一座宏大的革命博物馆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红枫，仍像当年那把红油纸伞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在红土地上陈列"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"故事很多很多"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解说词只四个字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“三湾改编”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}